{{main|Absalom (name)}}
*"Avshalom" (אבשלום) is commonly used as a male first name in contemporary [[Israel]]. Other variants, used either as a first name or a surname, include "Absalom", "[[Absolon (surname)|Absolon]]", "[[Avessalom]]", "[[Avesalom]]", "[[Absalon]]", and "[[Absolom (name)|Absolom]]".
*"Axel", "Aksel" and "Akseli" are common Germanic variants of "Absalom", which are used as male first names primarily in [[Germany]] and the [[Scandinavia]]n region.
